vsParam:
Anyway, what's your mother like, Totori?
Is she feminine and kawaii like you?

Uh, she is feminine sometimes,
but after all, she's an adventurer...

She once brought down an entire ruin while fighting a monster in it,
walked on the street with a monster...

And she struck down a monster as huge as a dragon
with just one blow. There are many such stories of her.
Oh, really? Sounds like a valiant woman...
She's not like you at all...

Thank you, [px]!
Actually, I also think she's pretty cool too...

Yeah...
I'm different from her. She's too powerful...
Anyway, your mother is the opposite of you, right?

Er, I bet your mother can easily accomplish adventures
you're taking on now...

I have one question...
Why are these all stories you heard?

To be honest, my mother went missing when I was
very little. I don't have a lot of memory of her...

But she's my goal... I want to become as powerful
as her before I see her again.

Uh!
You want to be like your mother, Totori!?

Everyone should have their own ways of living.
There's really no need to be like someone else, right?

Uh, hmm? So, er...
You think I'm wrong to make mother my goal?

Ha-ha...
We just would like to see you pursue your own life.
I wish you could see your mother one day...
